settings.description:
Goomba's shoes? Venus flytraps spewing up spiky balls? Nipper plants breathing fire? What is this, some sort of Mario game? 

Prod. Code - 103A/104A/106A - 6/22/22, Wed-11:45 am
A remake of Super Mario World 1-3. The rotating chain platforms aren't in SMB3, so several SMB1 Platforms have been added to help you collect coins.
A remake of Super Mario World 1-2. No Yoshi here, so Goomba Shoe is used instead.
While in his usual trips, Mario encounters a Bullet Bill field, filled to the brim with Bullet and Missile Bills. What powers and quirks will Mario find in his adventure?
